00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:00:06,520 --> 00:00:07,710
This is the near future.

3
00:00:08,700 --> 00:00:11,100
Gene editing technology has developed rapidly.

4
00:00:11,690 --> 00:00:14,290
A scientific life form called "humanoid"

5
00:00:14,660 --> 00:00:15,660
has been created.

6
00:00:16,920 --> 00:00:18,380
The physiological structure of humanoids

7
00:00:18,410 --> 00:00:20,290
is almost the same as that of humans.

8
00:00:20,850 --> 00:00:21,980
The only difference

9
00:00:22,050 --> 00:00:24,020
is that the neurons in their brains

10
00:00:24,270 --> 00:00:26,160
have been gene-edited in a certain way.

11
00:00:26,460 --> 00:00:30,240
They have a sole initial obsession that must be obeyed.

12
00:00:31,170 --> 00:00:32,680
They can be loyal spouses
until the end of their lives.

13
00:00:32,870 --> 00:00:34,210
They can be meek and filial children.

14
00:00:34,630 --> 00:00:36,140
They can be employees loyal to their boss.

15
00:00:36,420 --> 00:00:39,170
These custom-made humanoids started to circulate

16
00:00:39,250 --> 00:00:40,870
as commercial goods in the worldwide.

17
00:00:41,610 --> 00:00:43,500
Even in some countries where production

18
00:00:43,500 --> 00:00:45,180
and selling of humanoids are illegal,

19
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:46,790
there are still outlaws

20
00:00:47,070 --> 00:00:48,450
who bring

21
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:50,360
humanoids into their country without permission

22
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:51,660
and sell them secretly.

23
00:00:53,120 --> 00:00:54,670
Along with the wide spread of humanoids,

24
00:00:54,870 --> 00:00:56,330
their risks gradually emerge.

25
00:00:57,050 --> 00:00:58,230
More and more people

26
00:00:58,260 --> 00:00:59,070
started to be addicted to

27
00:00:59,100 --> 00:01:01,130
the fake emotions provided by humanoids.

28
00:01:01,990 --> 00:01:03,750
And for humanoids themselves,

29
00:01:04,200 --> 00:01:05,750
their thoughts and emotions

30
00:01:05,780 --> 00:01:07,960
are easily deformed

31
00:01:07,990 --> 00:01:09,130
under the restriction of the initial obsession.

32
00:01:09,440 --> 00:01:11,710
Many malignant incidents happened due to that.

33
00:01:13,350 --> 00:01:15,240
In the face of 
the more and more serious situation,

34
00:01:15,370 --> 00:01:17,470
the international society 
quickly held a meeting.

35
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:20,010
The production ban 
and the recall of humanoids

36
00:01:20,250 --> 00:01:21,250
were approved unanimously.

37
00:01:22,090 --> 00:01:22,970
According to the agreement,

38
00:01:23,110 --> 00:01:25,720
all nations will stop producing humanoids immediately.

39
00:01:26,330 --> 00:01:28,130
They should also recall and centrally manage

40
00:01:28,160 --> 00:01:30,240
all the humanoids in their country.

41
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:33,300
Sheen Genome Institute

42
00:01:33,320 --> 00:01:35,500
was established in Xiyuan City very quickly.

43
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:38,300
It's to cooperate with the police

44
00:01:38,330 --> 00:01:40,430
to search for and identify 
the humanoids in our country.

45
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:43,580
However, the process isn't going smoothly.

46
00:01:46,770 --> 00:01:48,380
The only way to identify a humanoid

47
00:01:48,380 --> 00:01:50,670
is to inject the identification drug

48
00:01:50,700 --> 00:01:52,870
and then observe if the pupils would change color.

49
00:01:53,330 --> 00:01:55,970
However, the identification drug is still defective.

50
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:58,600
It's very harmful to ordinary people.

51
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:02,220
Therefore, its use is strictly restricted.

52
