That day,

133
00:05:54,770 --> 00:05:56,020
I heard someone walking back and forth

134
00:05:56,050 --> 00:05:56,960
in the corridor.

135
00:05:57,330 --> 00:05:58,310
Then I heard someone

136
00:05:58,330 --> 00:05:59,470
knocking on every door.

137
00:05:59,909 --> 00:06:00,620
After that,

138
