You specialize in investigating humanoids.

218
00:10:00,660 --> 00:10:01,600
Then you should know

219
00:10:02,610 --> 00:10:03,500
the danger of humanoids, right?

220
00:10:05,180 --> 00:10:05,650
Ms. Chen,

221
00:10:06,690 --> 00:10:08,020
