Cheng Nuo.

237
00:13:14,790 --> 00:13:15,550
Fang Yuan.

238
00:13:15,700 --> 00:13:17,190
We are investigators from Sheen Genome Institute.

239
00:13:17,210 --> 00:13:18,130
No need to introduce us.

240
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:19,030
