453
00:21:27,860 --> 00:21:28,910
I don't blame her.

454
00:21:30,300 --> 00:21:32,890
But she actually wanted to spend more time with you.

455
00:21:33,380 --> 00:21:35,390
That's why she took you to a hot spring hotel.

456
00:21:36,050 --> 00:21:36,890
But

457
00:21:37,330 --> 00:21:38,990
what happened that day

458
00:21:39,950 --> 00:21:41,550
