459
00:21:41,880 --> 00:21:42,630
Right?

460
00:21:48,100 --> 00:21:48,790
Yuan.

461
00:21:49,050 --> 00:21:50,140
You're very brave.

462
00:21:51,280 --> 00:21:52,610
